---
import IconCompanies from "./IconCompanies.astro";
import IconStartup from "./IconStartup.astro";
---

<section class="flex flex-col bg-[#000423] md:min-h-dvh md:px-10">
  <div class="flex flex-col m-10 md:mx-0">
    <h2
      class="text-white text-center my-10 font-medium text-6xl md:text-4xl md:pt-0 md:my-10"
    >
      Our clients
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-10 mx-10">
      <div class="text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-950 rounded-xl p-10 mb-10 md:mb-0 md:max-w-[600px]">
        <div>
          <IconStartup />
        </div>
    
        <h3 class="py-6 font-bold text-5xl md:text-2xl">Startups</h3>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          Scientifica invests in startups and offers unparalleled access to
          cutting-edge science and technology that augment capabilities to allow
          business scale faster, stronger, and safer.
        </p>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          We have built a network of experts including scientists, technical and
          executive talent, top media, and marketing resources, as well as other
          technology decision-makers, influencers, and key opinion leaders.
        </p>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          Scientifica uses its network as part of its commitment to helping
          startups grow their business, so our operating teams provide
          entrepreneurs with access to expertise and insights across the entire
          spectrum of company building.
        </p>
      </div>
    
      <div class="text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-950 rounded-xl p-10 md:max-w-[600px]">
        <div>
          <IconCompanies />
        </div>
    
        <h3 class="py-6 font-bold text-5xl md:text-2xl">
          Established companies
        </h3>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          Scientifica launches and incubates advanced AI-First solutions in
          partnership with established companies giving these organizations
          unparalleled access to cutting-edge science and technology.
        </p>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          Carry out own exploration and build proprietary digital products in
          conjunction with partners and clients. The result of this exploration
          is the creation of digital products that adjust to the needs of the
          market. The products are validated in the market to understand that
          they have the possibility of generating income and can grow
          organically.
        </p>
    
        <p class="text-4xl md:text-base">
          Scientifica works on the creation of science-based products for
          different industries such as Financial & Insurance, Health, Arts,
          Sports, Media, Real Estate, Oil & Gas, Consumer, Agriculture, Mining,
          Aerospatiale, etc.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
</style>
